txt.en: The recipe needed to complete this quest is available for purchase. <rgb=#00f000>Purchase the quest recipe from the guild leader.</rgb>\n\nPack a crate of shields for Umbar Baharbêl.
Provide the crate of shields to the Umbar Metalsmith's Guild Leader.
Deliver a crate of shields to the Umbar Metalsmith's Guild Leader
Talk to the Metalsmith's Guild Leader in Umbar Baharbêl
'Most excellent. We will send these shields out to owners with great haste.'
Deliver a crate of shields to the Umbar Metalsmith's Guild Leader
Craft a crate of shields for the Umbar Metalsmith's Guild
Executed the recipe for a crate of shields
The metalsmith's guild in Umbar Baharbêl supplies armour and tools to the populace. You are tasked with assisting in meeting the demand.
Crafted a crate of shields for the Umbar Metalsmith's Guild
Execute the recipe for a crate of shields

'Whether it is armour for the guards, sea-farers, or anyone else who makes a request of the metalsmith's guild, we fill their orders. Demand increased with the rise of the Kindred and remains as high as ever.\n\n'As a member of our guild, we request your assistance in keeping our reputation as pure as the ore we use to craft our wares.'
